# Agent runtime config. NO inline comments after values (the loader keeps everything after '=').
# Autonomous agent: a continuously SELF-DRIVING worker. Unlike ops (which no-ops until the operator
# messages), each tick it reconstructs state from its own memory + work.json queue, picks the next
# highest-value step toward its MISSION, does it, records evidence, and updates memory — no human in
# the loop. INTERVAL_SECONDS is its heartbeat (3h here, not 24h); RUNTIME_MODE=daemon keeps it running.
# SUPERVISE=auto turns the in-container OFF-OPUS supervisor ON iff BRAIN=local (cheap planner + verify
# gate that keeps the queue full and escalates stuck items). Switch BRAIN=local and it kicks in
# automatically; with BRAIN=claude it stays off (the model plans its own queue each tick).
AGENT_ID=autonomous-agent
BRAIN=claude
MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-6
RUNTIME_MODE=daemon
INTERVAL_SECONDS=10800
PERMISSION=dangerous
TOOLS_ROOT=/workspace
SUPERVISE=auto
